s |last=Child |first=Ben |website=[[The Guardian]] |date=August 27, 2013 |access-date=September 27, 2019 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130827104006/http://www.theguardian.com/film/2013/aug/27/ben-affleck-signed-to-several-batman-films |archive-date=August 27, 2013 |url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"KravitzTHR\">{{Cite web |url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/batman-zoe-kravitz-nabs-catwoman-role-1247050 |title='The Batman': Zoe Kravitz to Star as Catwoman |last=Kit |first=Borys |website=[[The Hollywood Reporter]] |date=October 14, 2019 |access-date=October 14, 2019 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191014211405/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/batman-zoe-kravitz-nabs-catwoman-role-1247050 |archive-date=October 14, 2019 |url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"KravitzVariety\">{{Cite web |url=https://variety.com/2020/tv/news/zoe-kravitz-batman-catwoman-1203471015/ |title=Zoe Kravitz Teases 'The Batman' and Which Iconic Catwoman Performer Inspires Her |last=Thorne |first=Will |website=[[Variety (magazine)|Variety]] |date=January 17, 2020 |accessdate=January 21, 2020 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200121215010/https://variety.com/2020/tv/news/zoe-kravitz-batman-catwoman-1203471015/ |archive-date=January 21, 2020 |url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"WrightGordon\">{{Cite web |url=https://screenrant.com/batman-movie-cast-commissioner-gordon-jeffrey-wright/ |title='The Batman' Eyes Jeffrey Wright For Commissioner Jim Gordon Role |last=Hood |first=Cooper |website=[[Screen Rant]] |date=September 23, 2019 |access-date=October 14, 2019 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190924152307/https://screenrant.com/batman-movie-cast-commissioner-gordon-jeffrey-wright/ |archive-date=September 24, 2019 |url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"KravitzCast\">{{Cite web |url=https://deadline.com/2019/10/the-batman-finds-its-selina-kyle-in-zoe-kravitz-1202759926/ |title='The Batman' Finds Its Selina Kyle In Zo\u00eb K